      </userestrict>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_5dabc7db5c264ee89a4dada36f362424">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <prefercite id="aspace_d9288c6bf8ebcb418117025e40e14376">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>New York Architects/Frank Lupo Daniel Rowen Records (MS 1973).  Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
